EASTERN NORTH ATLANTIC.
SCOTLAND.
DNC 19.
1. HAZARDOUS OPERATIONS IN PROGRESS 0800Z TO 1800Z
   DAILY UNTIL 26 OCT IN AREA WITHIN
   55 MILES OF 57-22.4N 009-10.6W.
   VESSELS INTENDING TO ENTER AREA SHOULD
   CONTACT HEBRIDES RANGE CONTROL ON VHF CH 16
   OR PHONE: 187 060 4449 FOR ADVICE.
2. CANCEL THIS MSG 261900Z OCT 19.
